  "content": "<p>Grunts are the backbone of any good special forces unit. They are strong, confident, and capable of handling almost any threat. Grunts are the ultimate soldier&mdash;give them a job and they'll die trying to get it done. Grunts work best under a good Tactician.</p>\n<p>Grunts prefer to attack German forces head on, relying on superior training and firepower to win the day. Grunts are first into the fight and last to retreat. They are team players who are ready to pay the ultimate sacrifice for freedom.</p>\n<h2>Advancement</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"width: 503px; border-style: solid; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; height: 107px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 27px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>Level</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;XP</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;HD</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;BHB</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;ST</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">0</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">14</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2000</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">3 + 1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">13</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">4000</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">12</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">8000</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">5 + 1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">11</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">16000</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">10</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Abilities</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Combat Machine</li>\n<li>Uncanny Toughness</li>\n<li>Camaraderie (3rd level)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><br />Saving Throws</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Grunts receive a <strong>+2 </strong>bonus to Saving Throws vs. <strong>explosions</strong> and <strong>suppressive fire.</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><br />XP Bonus</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Grunts with a Strength of 13 or 14 receive a 5% Experience Bonus, and those with 15 or higher get 10%.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"
